OL,3,C'Go f*** yourself': Fan 'shocked' by
OL,4,Cemail from football league chairman
OL,6,FAn FC United of Manchester fan says he
OL,7,Fwas "shocked" after he received an
OL,8,Femail telling him to "go f***
OL,9,Fyourself" from Chair of the Northern
OL,10,FPremier League Mark Harris.
OL,12,FAled Duckfield says the expletive-
OL,13,Fladen email came as a response to his
OL,14,Fmessage, expressing his concerns about
OL,15,FFC United's home fixture being moved
OL,16,Fto a neutral ground.
OL,18,FThe email response read: "Thank you
OL,19,Ffor your lovely email. Now go f***
OL,20,Fyourself. Mark Harris."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
