OL,3,C'Go f*** yourself': Fan 'shocked' by
OL,4,Cemail from football league chairman
OL,6,FIt comes after FC United of Manchester
OL,7,Fissued a statement, informing fans
OL,8,Fthat their upcoming home fixture
OL,9,Fagainst Stockton Town, based in
OL,10,FTeeside, will be played at a neutral
OL,11,Fvenue - Curzon Ashton FC's The
OL,12,FTameside Stadium - at 7.45pm on 21
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FIt said: "This decision has been made
OL,16,Funder the powers granted to the Board
OL,17,Fin accordance with Rule 8.7.2 of the
OL,18,FFA Standardised Rules.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775855466
OL,3,C'Go f*** yourself': Fan 'shocked' by
OL,4,Cemail from football league chairman
OL,6,F"FC United of Manchester proposed an
OL,7,Falternative arrangement for the
OL,8,Ffixture, which was considered by the
OL,9,FBoard but not accepted."
OL,11,FFollowing the announcement, Northern
OL,12,FPremier League Chairman Mark Harris
OL,13,Fsaid: "The Board has determined that a
OL,14,Fneutral venue is the most appropriate
OL,15,Foutcome in this instance.
OL,17,F"The decision was made taking into
OL,18,Faccount the interests of both FC
OL,19,FUnited of Manchester and Stockton
OL,20,FTown."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
