CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775855466
OL,3,C'Go f*** yourself': Fan 'shocked' by
OL,4,Cemail from football league chairman
OL,6,FAled Duckfield reached out to the
OL,7,FChairman via email, calling the
OL,8,Fdecision "diabolical".
OL,10,FHe said: "There is a chance we could
OL,11,Fwin the league at this fixture as well
OL,12,Fand to take this away from our
OL,13,Fsupporters from being in our own
OL,14,Fground shows the incompetence and lack
OL,15,Fof governance present at the NPL.
OL,17,F"You clearly have an issue with us,
OL,18,Fmaybe it's because we know how to do
OL,19,Fthings properly
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
