FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1775855466
OL,3,C'Go f*** yourself': Fan 'shocked' by
OL,4,Cemail from football league chairman
OL,6,F"At a time when non League clubs
OL,7,Fstruggle with cashflow, your decision
OL,8,Fwill cost our club and also lose our
OL,9,Fusual match day revenue.
OL,11,F"You are also making a laughing stock
OL,12,Fout of the integrity of this
OL,13,Fcompetition. You are now
OL,14,Fdisadvantaging the other competing
OL,15,Fteams for the playoffs by providing an
OL,16,Fadvantage to Stockton."
OL,18,FHe said the board should be "ashamed
OL,19,Fof themselves", urging the chairman to
OL,20,Fstand down from the board.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
