OL,3,C'Go f*** yourself': Fan 'shocked' by
OL,4,Cemail from football league chairman
OL,6,FA Northern Premier League spokesperson
OL,7,Ftold ITV News "an immediate apology
OL,8,Fwas issued by MH via email".
OL,10,FThe controversy has seen calls from
OL,11,Ffans for Mr Harris to step down, with
OL,12,Fone fan calling the response "Totally
OL,13,Funacceptable".
OL,15,FAnother fan posted on X: "I smell a
OL,16,Fresignation. Disgraceful response".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
